    'listing.1.title': 'Olympus Mons Summit Lodge',
    'listing.1.desc': 'Perched atop the tallest volcano in the solar system, this luxury dome offers breathtaking views of the Martian plains stretching to the horizon. Watch dust storms roll in from the comfort of your radiation-shielded panoramic lounge.',
    'listing.2.title': 'Valles Marineris Canyon Retreat',
    'listing.2.desc': "Carved into the walls of the solar system's grandest canyon, this cozy habitat offers stunning geological vistas. Explore ancient riverbeds and search for microfossils with our guided expedition packages.",
    'listing.3.title': 'Sea of Tranquility Base Camp',
    'listing.3.desc': 'Stay where it all began! Located near the historic Apollo 11 landing site, this heritage-listed dome combines retro-futuristic charm with modern life support. Bounce around in 1/6th gravity and enjoy Earthrise every morning.',
    'listing.4.title': 'Cloud City Floating Station',
